# Web (`web/`)

## Stack

- **Vanilla JS + static HTML/CSS** only. `web/package.json` has no real build step — do not add TypeScript, bundlers (webpack/vite/esbuild), or SPA frameworks here unless the user explicitly requests it.

## Artefacts panel

- Keep **`ARTEFACT_TABS`** in `web/app.js` aligned with **`ARTEFACT_WHITELIST`** in `server/src/artefact-endpoint.ts`. Mismatched `file` values cause **400** responses in dev. When adding or renaming an artefact tab, update **both** files in the same change.

## Pipeline coupling

- UI refresh logic keys off **stage categories** from `server/src/pipeline-stages.ts`. New categories or artefact-producing stages may require matching updates in `web/app.js` (SSE triggers, tab wiring).
